    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and looks as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. Every aspect of the car, from the flawless exterior paint to the pristine interior upholstery, has been meticulously maintained. The engine runs perfectly, and all mechanical components are in peak operating condition. This is a rare find for a collector or buyer seeking a vehicle with zero compromises.",
