    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable, functional option for anyone needing a dependable daily driver. While mechanically sound, the exterior shows its age with several noticeable paint chips on the front bumper and a small door ding on the passenger side. Inside, the upholstery shows moderate wear, particularly on the driver\u2019s seat bolsters, and some of the plastic trim pieces have minor scuffs. It has been regularly serviced, though it lacks the pristine finish of a newer model. This car is perfect for someone prioritizing utility and value over cosmetic perfection.",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project seekers! This vehicle is looking for a fresh start and a dedicated new owner ready to bring it back to its former glory. While it currently needs significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a fantastic, budget-friendly entry point for someone who loves a hands-on restoration project!",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
